      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry using bovine blood as a blood analogue. Operating points span the clinical flow-speed envelope (2–6 L/min, 2000–4000 RPM). Geometry fidelity and operating point coverage judged sufficient for MRL 2. No characterization of environmental operating conditions (temperature range, EMI exposure, altitude-related pressure variation) was included in the relevance assessment; the validation activity relevance is evaluated solely on geometric and hydraulic similarity."
    },
