      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model selection justified with reference to published literature or sensitivity study.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark comparisons for rotating machinery at similar Reynolds numbers. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model used; model constants drawn from published calibration studies. Model form uncertainty estimated at ±12% based on literature survey of alternative constitutive models."
    },
    {
