      "acceptanceCriteria": "Key model inputs (viscosity, geometry tolerances, rotational speed) characterized with uncertainty bounds.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity assigned as 3.2 ± 0.2 mPa·s based on literature range for bovine blood at 22°C. Geometry dimensions drawn from nominal CAD with ±25 µm manufacturing tolerance applied. Rotational speed uncertainty ±0.5%. Fluid temperature was fixed at 22°C for all input sensitivity analyses; no sensitivity to the 18–26°C in-theatre temperature range was assessed, meaning the viscosity input uncertainty does not reflect the full deployment envelope."
    },
