      "rationale": "Simulation boundary conditions set to match measured laboratory values: inlet flow rate, outlet pressure, rotational speed, and fluid viscosity all matched within stated tolerances. Equivalency confirmed for the 22°C, atmospheric-pressure laboratory condition. Equivalency between simulation inputs and the broader deployment environment (18–26°C operating theatres, potential EMI affecting pump controller electronics, high-altitude reduced-pressure facilities) was not evaluated; the equivalency assessment is bounded to the single laboratory condition used in validation."
